data.description: Welcome to this charming brick home that has 1,510 square feet of spacious living space and sits on over an acre of land. Step inside, and you'll be immediately captivated by the open living room adorned with a beautifully beamed ceiling, which creates a light and airy ambiance. The focal point of the living room is a cozy wood-burning fireplace and adjacent formal dining area. The kitchen boasts ample counter space and cabinets. The pass-through windows in the kitchen add a touch of functionality and serve as a delightful accent, enhancing the overall entertaining experience. The main bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with dual vanities. Additionally, the ensuite has a spacious walk-in shower. One of the highlights of this property is the expansive backyard, which can be accessed through the covered back porch. The sheer size of the backyard has endless possibilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own! Schedule a private showing today.
